OL,3,CKiller requests whole-life term after
OL,4,Cattacks on inmates
OL,6,FA convicted murderer said he wants to
OL,7,Fspend the rest of his life behind bars
OL,8,Fafter admitting trying to kill two
OL,9,Fother inmates in top security prisons,
OL,10,Fa court has heard.
OL,12,FDuncan Heaton, 53, appeared by video
OL,13,Flink at Leeds Crown Court on Thursday
OL,14,Fwhere he admitted attempting to murder
OL,15,FDavid Minto at HMP Wakefield in
OL,16,FOctober last year.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
