OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776611465
OL,3,CKiller requests whole-life term after
OL,4,Cattacks on inmates
OL,6,FLast month, Heaton appeared at Hull
OL,7,FCrown Court where he admitted
OL,8,Fattempting to murder Andong Abong Ashu
OL,9,Fat HMP Full Sutton, near York, in May
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FAfter entering his guilty plea on
OL,13,FThursday, Heaton's barrister, David
OL,14,FGodfrey, told the court his client
OL,15,Fwanted his sentence to be "as long as
OL,16,Fpossible ` a whole life order".
OL,18,FMr Godfrey said: "He feels anxious
OL,19,Fabout any other form of sentence."
OL,26,@wD@[OUxD@^O]zD@ROU{D@bO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776611465
OL,3,CKiller requests whole-life term after
OL,4,Cattacks on inmates
OL,6,FThe barrister told the court there was
OL,7,Fno need for a psychiatric or any other
OL,8,Fform of report to be prepared before
OL,9,FHeaton can be sentenced.
OL,11,FHe said his client is currently held
OL,12,Fapart from other prisoners at
OL,13,FWakefield due to the risk he poses,
OL,14,Fand has seen only prison staff for
OL,15,Fmonths.
OL,17,FJudge Tom Bayliss KC told Heaton, who
OL,18,Fappeared on a screen from prison, he
OL,19,Fwill be sentenced at Leeds Crown Court
OL,20,Fon 6 May.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
