PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1776611465
OL,3,CKiller requests whole-life term after
OL,4,Cattacks on inmates
OL,6,FJudge Bayliss said: "It's going to be
OL,7,Fa life sentence. The issue will be the
OL,8,Fterm of that sentence."
OL,10,FHe said: "The case speaks for itself
OL,11,Fin terms of (Heaton's) risk."
OL,13,FHeaton, from Hull, is already serving
OL,14,Fa life sentence with a minimum term of
OL,15,F21 years and six months for the murder
OL,16,Fof Keith Opray in the city in 2014.
OL,26,@nD@UOUpD@WO]rD@JOUsD@MpmsD@VpnsD@]O]
