OL,3,CKiller requests whole-life term after
OL,4,Cattacks on inmates
OL,6,FAccording to reports of his sentencing
OL,7,Fat Hull Crown Court, disabled Mr Opray
OL,8,Fsuffered 43 stab wounds to his head,
OL,9,Fneck and body when he was attacked by
OL,10,Fthe defendant, who was a heroin addict.
